                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="menarinimaster/components/text"
                            text="&lt;em>&lt;span>&#xa;&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;width: 700px;&quot;>&#xa;    &lt;tbody>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.menarini.it/Portals/31/Images/notizie/MENARINI-GROUP-Logo-2017_300.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: left;&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td>&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/googlecloud.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Digitalizzazione, Menarini si affida a Google - Google Cloud&quot; style=&quot;float: right;&quot; />&lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;    &lt;/tbody>&#xa;&lt;/table>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;em>&lt;span>&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;em>&lt;span>The Menarini Group, a worldwide leader in the pharmaceutical industry, has chosen Google Cloud to help it work in a smarter and more flexible way, through the use of &lt;br />&#xa;G Suite which will allow its 17,000 employees to work together from anywhere in the world&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;em>&lt;span>&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;em>&lt;span>in real time and with the utmost ease&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;em>&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1CxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;em>&lt;span>Florence, 16 April 2018 -&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;span> &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.menarini.it/Home/Il-Gruppo&quot;>The &lt;strong>Menarini Group&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>, the leading Italian pharmaceutical company in the world with a presence in 136 countries, has announced a new partnership with &lt;strong>Google&lt;/strong> for a digital transformation project. At the heart of this journey is &amp;ldquo;smart working&amp;rdquo;, a new way of operating which is easier and more flexible. The 17,000 employees in the Group will be able to work together in real time across the world thanks to G Suite, Google Cloud&amp;rsquo;s business solution that allows companies to work together and share information.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1CxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>Menarini has always promoted the use of innovative technologies and decided on Google Cloud since it allows its personnel to work together faster and more effectively. G Suite is a series of different programmes which are accessible on different devices and which allow documents or work sheets to be accessed in real time. This allows for simultaneous editing of a single document shared within a team. The rest of the suite: Gmail for corporate email, the Calendar for organising meetings and Hangouts/Meet for business discussions and video conferences.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1CxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>In approximately six months the company has migrated all users in the Group to Google Cloud, launching a cultural and organisational change and supporting the productivity of individuals and work teams in the best way possible. The transition has been coordinated by Information and Communication Technology Management Team and The Group&amp;rsquo;s Organisational Development Team, using targeted measures designed to facilitate the process of adopting the new platform. Through G Suite a multi-lingual portal has also been made available, designed to help all personnel across the world through video tutorials, short instruction manuals and FAQs.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1CxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;em>&amp;ldquo;Investing in a secure, cutting-edge and efficient communications system was vital for a company like Menarini&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; &lt;/em>said &lt;strong>Alberto Giovanni Aleotti, Vice President of the Menarini Group&lt;em> &lt;/em>&lt;/strong>&lt;em>&amp;ndash; &amp;ldquo;With Google, more than 17,000 employees will be able to rely on an innovative, smart and protected platform&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em>.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;Normale1CxSpLast&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;em>&lt;span>&amp;ldquo;The new smart working models are in a state of constant development which will allow companies to leverage new technologies and make processes more efficient&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span>&lt;/em>&lt;span> &amp;ndash; added &lt;strong>Fabio Fregi, Country Manager for Google Cloud in Italy&lt;/strong> &amp;ndash; &lt;em>&amp;ldquo;Google Cloud&amp;rsquo;s solutions allow companies and personnel to work in step with the times and with a positive outlook towards the future. The Menarini Group&amp;rsquo;s decision is a winning move in the digital transformation of Italian companies.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;span>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>"
